### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = <pega_tu_token_aqui>
@productCategoryId = <pega_el_id_de_la_categoria>

### ─────────────────────────────
### PRODUCT CATEGORIES
### ─────────────────────────────

### Crear categoría (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/product-categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Gaseosas"
}

###

### Listar categorías
GET {{baseUrl}}/product-categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar categorías paginadas
GET {{baseUrl}}/product-categories?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar categorías activas
GET {{baseUrl}}/product-categories?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Buscar categorías por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/product-categories?q=gase
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener categoría por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/product-categories/one?productCategoryId={{productCategoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar categoría (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/product-categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{productCategoryId}}",
  "name": "Bebidas",
  "active": true
}

###

### Desactivar categoría (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/product-categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{productCategoryId}}",
  "name": "Gaseosas",
  "active": false
}

###

### Eliminar categoría (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/product-categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{productCategoryId}}"
}

###
